title: Spacious 9' ceilings, Stylish private cabanas, Ceiling fans included
neighborhood: 333 East Palmetto Park Road, Boca Raton, FL
posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Porcelain tile tub and shower surrounds', '-Spa-inspired bathrooms with quartz vanities and', 'under mounted sinks, double vanity available in select residences', '-Chef-caliber kitchens featuring 48-inch cabinets', '-Washer and dryer in every residence', '-51-bottle wine cooler in most residences', '-Electric car charging stations', '-Designer lighting and plumbing fixtures', '-Amazing views of Boca Raton, the Boca Raton Country Club and beaches from upper level residences', '-Gas ranges in Estate and Penthouse collection residences', '-Bike repair shop and interior bike storage', '-Dog park and dog wash station for our 4-legged residents', '-Resort-style swimming pool and sundeck with waterfall features', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
